{"id":"53a30f11eef0257b011e7f5b8d9708c4997e36cf4c4eeda092827d2025b6bcaf","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:0","text":"毛发梳理与渲染：Paul Sheehy"}
{"id":"26902896f1429c6478011cf765a7e7452341f487b15d3dc8706923f325de2ae4","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:1","text":"此 pattern 让艺术家能够创建易于控制的写实或艺术指导风格毛发和羽毛。只需少量控制项，就可以实现从人类赤褐色头发到幻想外星羽毛的效果。"}
{"id":"4156ba7e10b665d2566b03a88767b88b19dfb996e9752c2d3b65d77f40adf750","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:2","text":"通过对毛发纤维中的黑色素浓度建模，可以计算写实的人类毛发颜色。Melanin（黑色素）是一种深褐到黑色的色素，存在于人和动物的毛发、皮肤以及眼睛虹膜中。"}
{"id":"b3772874724bef28d8ab100ca8877b93d9c5632e15d60ced1dbaf5a3c6af4bb2","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:3","text":"octave_1octave_1"}
{"id":"7226bd18f7a93f28d2b00f7b1399aca0e8706049cef52afcde31e92caefd768a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:4","text":"这是基于 \"An Energy-Conserving Hair Reflectance Model\"（EGSR 2011，Eugene d’Eon、Guillaume Francois、Martin Hill、Joe Letteri、Jean-Marie Aubry）。"}
{"id":"8d59829c1e15afe1a7fae93e8e5e32d8511bec5fd598a09f4fea6033b31e8a66","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:5","text":"用法"}
{"id":"04671c69244e8e88b4d3161c2ac771321744d72d82fb21dd24ecc3ad9b68379e","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:6","text":"PxrHairColor 输出 3 个颜色，用于配合"}
{"id":"ccf31fc48275c143b867da4b33a4ee3f6d4e505c6b15e85616384686e98b23fe","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:36","text":"PxrMarschnerHair"}
{"id":"d1d94c415a47dec76d940a08006d57deda738574d2aef9eed14166cf9aad7f0c","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:8","text":"BxDF 提供物理上可信的结果。应按如下方式连接："}
{"id":"c643c5a80a3cd9ab74c89dc83eb1fc874e3f227a5ef536d14548b38d16702dac","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:9","text":"为了获得写实结果，PxrMarschnerHair 的"}
{"id":"cf136f858bebfa629ad4a1d80ef5f1862cc01a9100c4a2c9b33c117696654ed2","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:11","text":"应始终设为"}
{"id":"018fa96a44715c90bf93be148069cb28dd45d398f2cc75aa1565311f6e55d174","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:12","text":"白色"}
{"id":"e1c46e3d6f867bf398f910f37a4192998f11504fe3a361352fbacb10404f6729","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:13","text":"，同时使用 Physical 控制项"}
{"id":"2dc3d2a716261855f58cf7c2d9d8c12407a0ef4719d47106a79cacfa6bdad9a8","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:15","text":"使用 Artistic Mode 控制项时，建议在"}
{"id":"a78014cfe89e19823739fef5ad7e0a7f5736290ae753bfd6171ba5c3bcad9fb6","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:17","text":"材质上设置以下参数："}
{"id":"b4faf2504791f63188dcf7559d8de010d2a276a842f95c4faa23c3650613adf9","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:18","text":"diffuseGain 设为 1.0（Zinke 模型）"}
{"id":"cbe208d4cf227d04fdcb87573c0113ba6a02b8c3bfb972cfd59f23d14b7277f8","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:19","text":"specularGainR、specularGainTT、specularGainTRT、specularMixFresnel 和 specularEnergyCompensation 设为 1.0"}
{"id":"220f6ef45d2433544c0978097f0926f92219b18b511dc529d727da1058ab386d","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:20","text":"我们始终建议"}
{"id":"e9213756a2e67dcbd1524bf9382ab7ceb0622e1e19e25a7c999c1af81c18e52f","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:21","text":"至少"}
{"id":"ed1317cb4d2bd2aadeafa99c4df7ffac48f495c1918cf73a77dda78339cfbca8","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:22","text":"为漂亮的毛发设置 2 indirect bounces。设置位置为所选"}
{"id":"e43f447b65e6b1236fa237ffc613d5e0dde3509a5d3089e6378686e41318d17a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:23","text":"Integrator"}
{"id":"5e23ec6a300dc60a79641769017e16e9bf042cbd8fd0a54586a048ab9da972ff","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:26","text":"Mode"}
{"id":"afd8f05f040e832ad9a5a37aa995c8cbadc305725e1f75da25985f4eaf20aaf7","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:60","text":"Physical Mode"}
{"id":"b03f55a5eb47ed89d89bdaa3c7bbafe832c3b707547155f66d4d18ae874fbcae","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:28","text":": 这是默认控制集，会基于自然毛发颜色和响应提供写实结果。结合 Dye，用户可以创建任何可信的效果。这里期望颜色输入位于 sRGB color space。"}
{"id":"f2143d44db8ac414b13d59c58cd49b5698d0d59c3c919705da00e7f07300aed2","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:65","text":"Artistic Mode"}
{"id":"0d722e9019f70546f00a03a90b1063874578665d31da8671c0afafc0e445165f","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:30","text":": 此模式用 Color 选项替代 Melanin 控制项。虽然这可能产生不写实的结果，但能提供更大的艺术指导自由度。"}
{"id":"1367986aa8ccd6eb227709ce43e49673f87715a3b15e393ce6064b8ed47f586d","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:31","text":"Hair Color"}
{"id":"c17560bf5aa34bd51a1d0b216cc15e4ae31e553a4d63709bf1de7119128e7d03","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:33","text":"Melanin"}
{"id":"7d668e6c8c060f7820a4f1b517d9750ec4b9e171c42c13fa57c943892e6d8ee4","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:34","text":"您的浏览器不支持 HTML5 video 元素"}
{"id":"b40892a28326ac3cc8478332e4435fe93d51a796f705959c697089ed3d00066b","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:35","text":"毛发纤维中的黑色素浓度，范围为 0.0 到 1.0。0 会创建白色毛发，更高的值会创建更深的颜色。对于较浅的毛发，可能需要更多 Diffuse Gain，可在"}
{"id":"3abb4843a05157c16ecc88fb95b34a780be9ed4596118f131db4244a7b37f87f","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:37","text":"material 中设置。较深毛发可以使用较低值，最深色调甚至可使用 0.0。"}
{"id":"aeddff2a6bdf723fc438b7619fd929fe7dbb46cc881c674d10aa5e2d7b93cdc0","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:38","text":"Melanin Randomize"}
{"id":"539be7eeb78ece2d9cf76f83f23829d961c4241927550dc40054bb52e9d57a94","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:39","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则随机化黑色素浓度。"}
{"id":"f60491f8777728b66c7d2d54d70d364375d0e208d4c9260ceb9e0c76ab25b957","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:42","text":"可以选择 RGB 颜色，或使用另一个 pattern 为毛发提供任意颜色。渲染时会尽可能准确地复现所选颜色。"}
{"id":"75a2b09ec305c2b07264642b232e5385a1c18accf0c3b1a927c5bc93a6f4b60c","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:43","text":"Color Randomize"}
{"id":"e228bad33f013f94463251ace2fcb0debdfb900f24c7170e37a6c84954e5fc43","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:44","text":"使用 RGB 颜色或所选 pattern，可以提供随机颜色，与上方选择的颜色混合。"}
{"id":"e7d790d57e11e6ff0ec425749c24eee56338d4b51ba4d2753dd2084a0bdb1b47","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:45","text":"Darken Roots"}
{"id":"d6cf97dfcd74c522fd2edd1786b79ef0edb37d0ae0e3e8160b63f577b5ff9a21","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:46","text":"通过逐步增加黑色素，让毛发纤维根部逐渐变暗。该值对应根部额外增加的黑色素量。可使用"}
{"id":"9d930adeb2b6398dee622dfc783566b9c2e3a377fdaf099b9d2b0a6fca721dfa","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:53","text":"Darken Slope"}
{"id":"b21caa2405fd47ada103e2f0f6e20a5773f4c9d5393ebb6c65a4d7219164a655","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:49","text":"Darken End Position，"}
{"id":"19932b355dd940d09230c6db0de41e885af274acfb5fd230a12847b3b8bd8a0a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:50","text":"下面我们通过"}
{"id":"dd7c67b74bb66af0c9a60b86df98dab03ea381e43381610979a537c28fb81f20","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:51","text":"Darken End Position"}
{"id":"905ef7e718509a9423cee3c278a89818a2d95921d4d8bd136e48e1db8934eb00","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:52","text":"设为 1.0 来让整根毛发变暗。"}
{"id":"e25649b351370d5afa8a6bb72e5f5a3de43826e50c0f1d09ce19aefd6f4fbd04","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:54","text":"调整变暗的斜率。这会控制从深色到浅色的过渡。"}
{"id":"17a79a386e9d3090341b2ed4129c07c71fd20ef72e5bacc3a15df531f30f0714","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:55","text":"Darken End Position"}
{"id":"de04793f6c00c78772411bfd66cb353d1ea5028423e18028f30fc94cfd6ae401","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:56","text":"大多数情况下，变暗应发生在接近根部的位置，并保持其余毛发不变。end position 默认值为 0.5，因此只有前半段毛发会变暗。正确范围是 0. 到 1.0"}
{"id":"f7d0ae423e78019ec73ad01b4335c715124372fde6a0a9a4991b257b72f8c9e5","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:57","text":"Stray Hair Color"}
{"id":"86dfd556f736317b1493d863ba95763eacd7ea7997046513547a29beefa35ece","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:58","text":"Stray Density"}
{"id":"7b12d47c5904991c19e274d0b1723ea3e515a2398c5bfd4be06e055484938357","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:59","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则此项控制离散毛发出现的频率。白色离散毛发通常会在人开始变老或承受非常高压力时出现。"}
{"id":"ccd0fc584b51fdb5b459e8c4155d7b824b3bf34f57d854903c9b1cc2230caddf","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:61","text":"Stray Melanin"}
{"id":"14bdfbae41e90664124c42f43635988e946171243696d2f1db2e9b68b735fb71","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:62","text":"离散毛发的黑色素浓度。它的工作方式类似主 Melanin 参数，可用于控制结果颜色。"}
{"id":"d07788d9ae5bf154adc5a9940d6f8555973c9708b406974ccf8817a106feb291","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:63","text":"Stray Random Melanin"}
{"id":"a9e13b5660becd3e7d973910747431e122416a859122de3e90f876754600e9a9","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:64","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则随机化离散毛发的黑色素级别。"}
{"id":"9f9fab8b9abcc62017bff98f372d6513ba43c8ec09e0bff2e847eaa06bc942d5","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:66","text":"Stray Color"}
{"id":"254ceb8aeb205cce160e15eadc7976166f118b1e91c543f7cfb0cc3aff1e2a10","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:67","text":"可为离散毛发颜色选择任意 RGB 颜色或 pattern。下面 Color 为白色，离散毛发使用纯色或 ramp 着色。Stray Density 设置为 0.5"}
{"id":"0d55bc4423d10c70e3113f99b335cfb3d33140f8863e47a36978bddd64a5fa2a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:68","text":"Stray Random Color"}
{"id":"88b8a9bb22a08c338c56cb9e4df95f45cdba1d2e87bdaa00ca61bb6420c49a46","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:69","text":"可选择任意 RGB 颜色或 pattern，用于随机化并组合离散毛发颜色。下面颜色设置为 black/none、dark red、red。Hair Color 选择为 blue。Stray Density 设置为 0.5"}
{"id":"65e26cd3da7f5c0049e9a660505450a4d1f730473564193b06584ecd591c26b3","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:70","text":"Dye Color"}
{"id":"5930c048f31bad10da285d8e03e93e385dd4f0f93468695dfccc43d34da00c41","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:71","text":"Dye"}
{"id":"ef75f62bea46677e11643c9635896bb84adf8900c3e69f60d427e034f7b0e7a3","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:72","text":"毛发可以用颜色染色。该颜色会以可信方式与毛发颜色结合。第一个示例中，毛发非常深，因为红发上的深蓝色染剂会产生这种颜色。更纯的饱和颜色，或在黑色素设置为 0.0 的毛发上选择的颜色，会得到更鲜艳的颜色，例如红色示例。"}
{"id":"5a5175155c421ad8287d1af5bc20cd39e5394f512be3ff1a4f4ca3691dfc3d0a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:73","text":"Dye Random Hue"}
{"id":"76bbcf586fe88322662df983fd6511e94e85109000ccc3649c1bf9806ba21a31","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:74","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则随机化染剂色相。下面使用无黑色素的毛发和绿色染剂，然后逐步增加随机化。注意，此结果可以是任何类型的随机颜色，而随机黑色素控制项只会产生某种形式的可信毛发颜色。"}
{"id":"4a992a7c3b28d862899ceb5a8f235c41805ca309d1b89d4150de639ce56f349a","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:75","text":"Dye Random Saturation"}
{"id":"d3a0bd9d398195ce11baafd95ef8e5f7ec8a03ae6984890d57a2dda11b7bcb77","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:76","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则随机化染剂 saturation。较低的 saturation 会显露设置好的毛发黑色素颜色。你可能会发现需要高于 1.0 的值，才能让更多毛发降低饱和度；也可以将 Random Pivot 参数提高到 0.5 以上，当此 Random 参数设得很高时，1.0 可能会完全消除 Dye Color。"}
{"id":"b8730bf4e89448c5551fbc03557a2662dcaf3ad29c1591ca688b0e5e31946a40","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:77","text":"Random Setup"}
{"id":"69eaa33622cbb95b830f3b82750d7ac2832dcf06e96f7358fbc708064797f981","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:78","text":"Hair ID Primvar"}
{"id":"3b9c89d2960dcde9c59617c81e572549aecde93a071bae297c518a555c9000fc","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:79","text":"如果 hairIndexPrimvar 为空，所有随机化选项都不会工作！你可能会在 Maya 中看到警告，这是因为 shader ball 预览没有这样的 primvar，因此其预览渲染可能会生成错误。"}
{"id":"676b0b520b2d26d4c843a3edb7ff8a59edac9618782bc4a51fe80e2ac78fa0f9","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:80","text":"以下是已知 primvars 列表："}
{"id":"c86ae63afba6e8ca810703a21d476c3e7689ac1b9429f68b587be7fca2edd4d2","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:81","text":"Hair Generator"}
{"id":"164e4479fff3cbd18d29a3bd55a5a55157a4066950b0ac94f9addbe7790a4538","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:82","text":"Primitive Variable"}
{"id":"efc88ef96d563b5988ec01790e003d61bd0d987d4c2921c3ee45a867f7aae5a9","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:83","text":"Maya Hair/Fur"}
{"id":"1bc04b5291c26a46d918139138b992d2de976d6851d0893b0476b85bfbdfc6e6","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:92","text":"index"}
{"id":"9d022ff6456e24cf0a26ba261961b9bb6d99c1be15ad29b75f123ad2b4c22b86","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:85","text":"Maya Xgen"}
{"id":"9e966670f8fd14080c86e69d8c271f82d4ec23c8f5cc5dd7676b05710e5ce66e","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:86","text":"id_XP"}
{"id":"7ca0e69e1426e70a310d50ca3ae58cbcfba1ec0fdf5052041c1ae9b86462b456","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:87","text":"Yeti"}
{"id":"cdb600026d934759ecfc216d14c0add6fc1eaaeaa0258e3a787225b95321e97f","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:88","text":"fur_id"}
{"id":"a56145270ce6b3bebd1dd012b73948677dd618d496488bc608a3cb43ce3547dd","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:90","text":"id"}
{"id":"5a89e19503e9e573a54f514baaf648ba96fb0be865498d895f9243a1ce396a2d","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:93","text":"Random Pivot"}
{"id":"40cb2e79e572e5ddbc4e5c0e22516493a6f4c0612a9b96758ac4c46cfa908df0","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:94","text":"Offset（偏移）随机值，让你可以创建居中、加性或减性的随机变化。"}
{"id":"023cb80bf5be3a793b61ac3415376a7fc0bf9c732689b663c27654cbbedba04e","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:95","text":"Randomization"}
{"id":"7a47788bafbef5879907b2183855f8402e20b18f3346f6161068eb41996ac417","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:96","text":"Pivot Value"}
{"id":"765fc5369dc160b0f53b8ec816df03d3e47557e07b0f158a88b1164980d3cdd6","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:97","text":"Additive"}
{"id":"739dee74b4dc70aad2beadd6e517161cfb8431f81c0870b43a0be05a54cb9267","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:98","text":"Centered"}
{"id":"12a8914e1bf551f556d1d1411c8960b34d29775b0123e4d0b6f30c441fde7aa0","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:99","text":"Subtractive"}
{"id":"c740e9da589e5a5ebbfc961088d707c0f2ec9f01a213206a203a1d9e50e86650","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:100","text":"Random Seed"}
{"id":"4ec0efd01bf0a448eb59ef5a853feae38c96e70d766c474c6474428174fbb42d","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:101","text":"global（全局）Random Seed，用于确保得到不同的随机结果。如果有重复的 groom，但需要通过随机参数获得不同着色，这尤其有用。"}
{"id":"852434037f7d0467c7c0b2d6e25f7effdbbe1c99414c6460a42f5ab0821cf3b6","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:102","text":"View Index Random"}
{"id":"761124e7873d2b0a7a8e514fc7782647b9e325913af069e7c01ebe73431b9879","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:103","text":"如果定义了 hairIndexPrimvar，则将每条曲线的随机值作为 Output（输出）。这是一个调试开关，用于检查 Hair ID primitive variable 是否已正确设置。下面是正确 ID 的示例。"}
{"id":"0898f8cd8150d83cb9fc35f17fa70672a3ad3ca9725739cb3f7ec1716975678d","item_id":"bcdd4a0295:104","text":"毛发梳理与渲染作品：Paul Sheehy"}
{"id": "96ebc01281e6f2f2ad39d2a90689f4e98ea8df50458590e5b7974565c909a0c5", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:10", "text": "Primary Specular Color"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:14", "text": "。"}
{"id": "e68b36b17cbd990802f57741cb75cf3a73fa66a61999b0cd70e3cf7d26cfb25f", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:25", "text": "Parameters（参数）"}
{"id": "6b73191a0a4b67420e61d51c9f207c35277eaf18fbbf5beb52a320a23fe09653", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:41", "text": "Color"}
{"id": "6201111b83a0cb5b0922cb37cc442b9a40e24e3b1ce100a4bb204f4c63fd2ac0", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:48", "text": "和"}
{"id": "ae2e32e94fed2644afb40662216566d5fc3f1bbdafa9ea0cbeacaef8284e9c69", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:89", "text": "Houdini"}
{"id": "f333db1a7e319b794d791112d0b7df2b8bd85c83f8ad46d84b05f966d45074ec", "item_id": "bcdd4a0295:91", "text": "Blender"}
